Outdoors, the partially fenced backyard provides a private space for entertaining and a detached single car garage for additional parking or storage. Take advantage of the city's additional second ADU income opportunities!
nearby_schools: Bellingham Public Schools, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Opportunity Knocks Priced to Personalize! Heres your chance to make this condo truly your own. This 2 bed/1.5 bath condo is in need of cosmetic updates/repairs. Unit is priced 35k less than other comparable units in the complex to allow for updates including new carpeting/flooring, painting, appliances etc. Ground floor, end unit has a wonderful layout with spacious living area and large primary bedroom/bath with walk-in closet. Deck off kitchen to have your morning coffee and serene nature preserve/pond view from the living area. Individual storage unit in parking area. 55+ Community has a Clubhouse offering social activities, mailroom etc. Close to restaurants, shopping, medical facilities and parks.

Lightly wooded corner lot within walking distance to Alderwood Elementary School. Quick access to everything Bellingham has to offer. Buyer to verify gas, electricity, and build ability. City has communicated to the sellers that city water and sewer hook-up is not available at this time.

ELEGANT DESIGN WITH SPACIOUS LIVING Discover this thoughtfully crafted home featuring dramatic ceilings and a generous open layout, ideal for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying everyday life. Large, oversized windows invite an abundance of natural light while offering picturesque views of a peaceful conservation area just beyond your backyard, providing both privacy and serenity. A unique highlight of this property is the expansive yard a true rarity within city boundaries. This versatile space is perfect for outdoor activities, relaxation, or creative projects, all while benefiting from the convenience of city utilities. This is your chance to own a bright, modern sanctuary with standout features that are hard to find within the city.

Discover this charming 4-bed, 2-bath home with modern updates, renovated bathrooms, original hardwood floors, and fresh new carpet throughout. The dream kitchen features quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and custom cabinetry. Recent updates include a new roof, water heater, and furnace, ensuring comfort and efficiency. Enjoy an additional 572sqft of finished space with its own kitchen, bath, and ACideal for guests. Outdoors, the property spans nearly 2 acres with breathtaking Mt. Baker views, a barn (200 amp service) with horse stalls, raised garden beds, and a fenced backyardperfect for privacy and outdoor living. A true retreat for those seeking comfort and tranquility!

Better than NEW in this beautifully maintained 4-bedroom home in the heart of Sudden Valley! This spacious 2, 593 sq ft home offers an open-concept layout w/ tons natural light, peaceful greenbelt views & seamless indoor-outdoor flow. The kitchen is ideal for entertaining; featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry & an eating bar. Main floor den/office + another flex space, perfect for playtime, music, exercise & more! Upstairs, generously sized bedrooms + laundry + study nook. Terraced back yard, fenced w/ fire pit, your new relaxing oasis! Enjoy serene living just minutes from Lake Whatcom. Sudden Valley Community offers: parks, dog parks, hiking trails, boat launch, golf course, community center & more!

Welcome to your personal oasis on 2 acres, with 60 feet of private lakefront and a dock. The home has been beautifully updated with new countertops, refreshed flooring, interior paint, and a striking floor-to-ceiling Carrara marble tile fireplace, along with a brand-new roof. Enjoy stunning lake views from the living spaces, as well as the covered wraparound ironwood porch and back deck. Less than 5 minutes to Lake Whatcom Park and Chanterelle trailheads, and 15 minutes to Bellingham services and amenities, this home offers a lovely blend of secluded privacy and access to Whatcom County's famous outdoor lifestyle!
